      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 is deployed under a documented SQA plan conforming to ISO 9001:2015. Version control via Git with tagged release branches; regression test suite of 412 benchmark cases executed at each release. Achieved level 3 reflects documented SQA with independent audit trail."
